  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Early Childhood Care and Development in Rural Herat Province, Western Afghanistan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Identification and enrolment of 390 children from 13 villages of Injil district

Equip 13 ECCD centres with educational materials and visual aids

Liaise with government schools and facilitate enrolment of those children who completed ECCD to primary school

Build 18 community greenhouses (13 greenhouses attached to the previously established ECCD centres and 5 greenhouses attached to the 5 new ECCD centres)

Conduct 3 day agriculture training for 180 mothers from 13 previously established ECCD centres and the 5 new additional centres</narrative>
  </description>
